  "text": "When the catalyst of the man is processed by the energy, the experience of the man results. There are subtle misdirections in this simple statement having to do with the overriding the qualities of the significance. It is so that catalyst yields experience, however, through free will and the faculty of imperfect memory. Catalyst is most often only partially used and the experience, thus correspondingly skewed.",
